No. 09-894. Matthew Cate, Secretary, California Department of Corrections and Rehabilitation, Petitioner v. Mohammed Haroon Ali. 559 U.S. 1045, 130 S. Ct. 2065,

176 L. Ed. 2d 429,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2888. March 29, 2010.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 584 F.3d 1174.
